   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-a" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>He's not my rival. </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>You were just a newbie when you first came to Calderock Village. But look at you now... you are a respectable adventurer who receives challenges from a rival on a regular basis.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-a" image="QN_NPC_Warrior_Chandler.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-b" mid="12" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Stop it!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>Hahaha! Don't be shy!!<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Chandler pats your head with his big hands.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-c" mid="14" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> (Chandler continues to talk) </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>Don't be shy!<BR>Everyone needs a rival!<BR>Having a rival is a must in being a hero.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-d" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>The path of a hero is a hard and lonely one.<BR>Often times, even your allies won't able to soothe the loneliness and the pain.<BR>However, the only person who is on the same path as you is none other than... your rival</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-acceptted" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>Only your rival can understand that pain. Sometimes you feel closer to your rival than your family members and even your lover. I still remember when I met my destined rival.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-1-a" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> I'm busy right now, I do not have time for your old stories </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>About couple decades ago... it was when countless monsters swarmed into Calderock Village. In their frontline was this incredibly huge Orc.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-1-b" mid="26" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Chandler grabs your shoulders with his monstrous hands and continues on with the story.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>Just listen. All this will be your flesh and blood.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-1-c" mid="28" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Sounds like you will propose to that Orc next.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>Everyone around me was afraid of that Orc. But not me... my heart started beating faster, my nostrils got bigger, and my breathing became harder. And I couldn't say a word because my mouth was too dry.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-1-d" mid="30" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> (Doesn't really care about your response) </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Proposal</FONT>? It was exactly like that. It was as if... I met my soulmate. I knew at that moment that the Orc was to become my <FONT color=#a82424>destined rival</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-1-e" mid="32" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Somehow the story seems to get increasingly dangerous.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>It was as if that Orc recognized me also. That Orc... he charged towards me, with his face blushing in deep blue. I can never forget the feeling of his breath brushing against my cheeks.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-2" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Just skip everything and go directly to the end.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>Hah, what a kid. You will soon experience such... thrill.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Don't really want to experience that...)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-2-a" mid="37" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Typhoon Kim... that's quite the name for an Orc.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>I kept encountering that Orc from that day on. Along the way, I learned that his name was <FONT color=#a94407>Typhoon Kim</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-2-b" mid="39" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Maybe he died in battle elsewhere?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>Thanks to those battles with <FONT color=#a94407>Typhoon Kim</FONT>, I was able to further hone my skills. But I stopped seeing <FONT color=#a94407>Typhoon Kim</FONT> in battles.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-2-c" mid="41" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>There's no way that my <FONT color=#a82424>fated rival</FONT>, <FONT color=#a94407>Typhoon Kim</FONT>, could have fallen to the hands of another!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-2-d" mid="43" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Like I was saying, this story is getting too dangerous...)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>I felt lonely in a battle without <FONT color=#a94407>Typhoon Kim</FONT>. I realized what a significant part <FONT color=#a94407>Typhoon Kim</FONT> played in my life.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-2-e" mid="45" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> Whew, I'm sure there is nothing like that. </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>That's what a rival is. A true <FONT color=#a82424>god-given opponent</FONT> who is meant to bring you up to a higher state. A <FONT color=#a82424>non-identical twin bound by soul</FONT>. Anyways, congratulations for finally having someone like that.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-2-f" mid="47" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(...)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>Hah, I guess you were impressed by my story.<BR>You don't have to thank me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-2-f" image="QN_NPC_Warrior_Chandler.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>I guess you were so impressed that you are speechless. Hahaha!<BR>Remember what I told you today!<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(It appears that you've gotten closer to Master Warrior Chandler.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
